snippet.title: The Golf Club VR
snippet.description:
HB Studios is proud to present, The Golf Club VR for the HTC Vive available by the end of 2016. 

Stay tuned for more videos and information!

Full press release : http://thegolfclubgame.com/2016/10/05/golf-club-vr-htc-vive/
